The 'wc' command counts the amount of lines, words and characters in a file.
wc newfile.txt - This will display the amount of lines, words and characters in 'newfile.txt'
wc -l newfile.txt - This will display the amount of lines in 'newfile.txt'
wc -w newfile.txt - This will display the amount of words in 'newfile.txt'
wc -m newfile.txt - This will display the amount of characters in 'newfile.txt'
